art, Inverness-shire, Écosse, fille de Catherine Macintosh. Elle a eu au moins 4 fils et 4 filles avec Hector Roy - Eachainn Ruadh Mackenzie 1st of Gairloch. Elle est décédée en 1560, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 76 ans."},"de":{"about 1485–1560":"um 1485–1560","1485–1560":"1485–1560","1460–1528":"1460–1528","1500–Female":"1500–Verstorben","1504–Female":"1504–Verstorben","1507–Male":"1507–Verstorben","1510–1550":"1510–1550","1515–Male":"1515–Verstorben","1516–1550":"1516–1550","–Female":"Verstorben","1550":"1550","1560":"1560","1460":"1460","Abt 1504":"um 1504","about 1507":"um 1507","8 September 1528":"8. September 1528","about 1516":"um 1516","1500":"1500","1510":"1510","about 1515":"um 1515","1485":"1485","about 1500":"um 1500","1507":"1507","about 1485":"um 1485","1528":"1528","1516":"1516","1515":"1515","1504":"1504","Gairloch, Ross-shire, Scotland":"Gairloch, Ross-shire, Scotland","Moidart, Inverness-shire, Scotland":"Moidart, Inverness-shire, Scotland","Ross-shire, Scotland":"Ross-shire, Scotland","Dornie, Cromartyshire, Scotland":"Dornie, Cromartyshire, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Anne MacDonald wurde um 1485 in Moidart, Inverness-shire, Scotland, als Tochter von Catherine Macintosh geboren. Sie hatte mit Hector Roy - Eachainn Ruadh Mackenzie 1st of Gairloch mindestens 4 Söhne und 4 Töchter. Sie starb 1560 im Alter von 76 Jahren in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"about 1485–1560":"about 1485–1560","1485–1560":"1485–1560","1460–1528":"1460–1528","1500–Female":"1500–Desede","1504–Female":"1504–Desede","1507–Male":"1507–Desede","1510–1550":"1510–1550","1515–Male":"1515–Desede","1516–1550":"1516–1550","–Female":"Desede","1550":"1550","1560":"1560","1460":"1460","Abt 1504":"about 1504","about 1507":"about 1507","8 September 1528":"8 September 1528","about 1516":"about 1516","1500":"1500","1510":"1510","about 1515":"about 1515","1485":"1485","about 1500":"about 1500","1507":"1507","about 1485":"about 1485","1528":"1528","1516":"1516","1515":"1515","1504":"1504","Gairl